{"tid":1471080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【感化大陸撚】 YOUTUBE、殘體文宣 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T18:13:11.000Z","uid":198991,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6162ac4458d4e5e53f0b09657d85cebfb2a112","tid":1471080,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"因工作關係接觸唔少大陸人，前幾日終於忍唔住喺一個幾百人既行家微信群組開佢地波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n竟然....... 原來有唔少 (約兩成人) 其實係真正明白香港發生緊咩事，又有三成人係典型五毛，其餘一半就完全無出聲<br />\n<br />\n共通點係，五毛同果兩成人其實都有翻牆睇YOUTUBE，RTHK直播、直頭CAP 晒圖去話自己睇到所謂既真相<br />\n<br />\n所以YOUTUBE 同殘體文宣其實係要KEEP 住UPDATE，眼見好多得幾十人SUBSCRIBE YOUTUBER 都比佢地引用。 FACEBOOK 有用既片都要放埋上YOUTUBE，文宣組用埋殘體，千祈唔好以為完全無用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後跪求以下殘體文宣圖：<br />\n<br />\n1) 污國徽、掉國旗落海 其實係班狗做<br />\n2) 以往撐警吹雞後大量國旗掉塞滿垃圾桶<br />\n3) 811 班狗銅鑼灣拉人，衣著同示威者一樣<br />\n4) 尋晚兩個公安帶頭搞事/示持支威，扮示威者既狗UC制止佢地<br />\n5) 環時記者 - 黑工/無記者證/講英文/扮遊客/其實示持示威 </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後，818天安門見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Jzeuge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Jzeuge.jpg&h=43e0f2a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fbd3ca3981f7a0043037f8830048687e594a7a6","tid":1471080,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:47:02.000Z","msg":"自推 10 連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafa7f6198db6a1abdcfa9564e5e13e0e68cc658","tid":1471080,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"自推 10 連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755ed924c66589b58dfd23ddf6dc55a5a0b5e6fc","tid":1471080,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"自推 10 連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456f0df4ae8ed782624368918b6c4585585c79d7","tid":1471080,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n一定要反攻內地文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca69403b7591f60ad32134240222e6ea6c40ab9","tid":1471080,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"自推 10 連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d151e9126f2079fddbaa94935dbfc2920d10f300","tid":1471080,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"4) &amp; 5) &quot;支持示威&quot;<br />\n<br />\n屌 打錯晒D 字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194e39ff848cdc894d2eed28ea7957e15694e8fd","tid":1471080,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"自推 10 連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa194c6d1721dbd27329632ed33ffdf458fd54dd","tid":1471080,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservic